no matter
the rules of engagement.

06:48.908 --> 06:52.345 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MAN: He's already spent a year
in jail dealing
with this.

06:52.379 --> 06:54.281 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
His family has been broken.

06:54.314 --> 06:55.715 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
His father had a stroke.

06:55.749 --> 06:57.217 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
His mother has collapsed.

06:57.250 --> 06:59.719 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
