that was
trying to sail to Italy.

07:32.686 --> 07:36.690 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Officials say more bodies are
still floating
offshore.

07:36.723 --> 07:41.261 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Back in this country, hundreds
of people in
Northern California were forced
to evacuate

07:41.294 --> 07:46.599 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
