sent creeks
and rivers flowing over their
banks.

07:46.633 --> 07:52.605 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
In San Jose, fire crews carried
out a series
of rescues as water levels
surged.

07:52.639 --> 07:58.044 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
One rescue came near a homeless
encampment
amid reports that up to 40
people might be

07:58.078 --> 08:00.013 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
