Department: Normally,
that's only three or four feet
deep out there,

08:01.715 --> 08:03.717 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
but that water is not where it
normally sits.

08:03.750 --> 08:05.685 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
