is.

08:05.719 --> 08:08.922 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
All of the water in the Coyote
Creek watershed
right now is dangerous.

08:08.955 --> 08:10.423 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
It's swift moving.

08:10.457 --> 08:14.127 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
