contaminated.

08:15.962 --> 08:20.600 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Authorities say
it may take
four days or longer for the
rivers to begin

08:20.633 --> 08:22.435 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
to fall.

