Environmental Protection
Agency, Scott Pruitt, struck a
conciliatory

08:27.207 --> 08:29.109 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
tone today.

08:29.142 --> 08:35.215 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
