21:38.864 --> 21:41.800 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JONATHAN GREENBLATT: Well, look,
the ADL has
been tracking anti-Semitic
attitudes since

21:41.834 --> 21:43.636 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
