conversation.

22:11.530 --> 22:18.604 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We saw images and ideas from
white supremacists
literally shared from political
campaigns

22:18.637 --> 22:22.107 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
