of major news
organizations.

22:22.141 --> 22:24.710 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
We saw it in our political
rallies as well.

22:24.743 --> 22:28.614 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And then, after the election,
there was a
surge of hate crimes.

22:28.647 --> 22:34.520 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
