country.

22:43.262 --> 22:48.968 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, I think what's happened is,
the extremists
feel emboldened.

22:49.001 --> 22:54.506 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The lack of comments from the
highest levels
of our political office have
created a vacuum

22:54.540 --> 22:59.878 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
