has reached an incredibly high
level.

23:37.583 --> 23:39.518 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JOHN YANG: What do you want to
see him do?

23:39.551 --> 23:41.353 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JONATHAN GREENBLATT: Well, there
