of things.

23:41.387 --> 23:46.525 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We think it's time for the
president to announce
steps for the White House to
undertake.

23:46.558 --> 23:52.564 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
