that and to
work with U.S. attorneys around
the country.

24:08.580 --> 24:11.884 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Attorney General Sessions should
get that
started immediately.

24:11.917 --> 24:16.989 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Number two, we'd like to see a
White House
task force on hate crimes.

24:17.022 --> 24:20.826 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
This could be something again
