the country.

24:37.843 --> 24:43.882 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And we need to make sure that
every law enforcement
agency and officer understands
how to deal

24:43.916 --> 24:45.284 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
