25:11.844 --> 25:15.848 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, the attorney general could
push and the
president could push governors
and state attorney

25:15.881 --> 25:21.086 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
generals to move forward with
hate crimes
laws all over America to protect
the Jewish

25:21.120 --> 25:23.288 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
community and other marginalized
groups.

25:23.322 --> 25:25.457 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JOHN YANG: We have got about a
