positives, instead
of fighting, because...

29:23.829 --> 29:25.464 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Good.

29:25.497 --> 29:30.135 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
