support my family, make good
money, you know,

41:30.221 --> 41:34.726 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
have something in life.

41:34.759 --> 41:46.637 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DAVE BOUNDS: I cherish the days
