about what you
do before you do it.

44:51.422 --> 44:57.395 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHARLAYNE HUNTER-GAULT: But you
also begin
to close doors -- well, close
spaces between

44:57.428 --> 45:00.398 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
