children and Latin
children.

45:00.431 --> 45:02.266 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Tell me how you did that.

45:02.300 --> 45:05.369 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LEMUEL LAROCHE: Adults are
programmed in their
own viewpoints, their political
views, their

45:05.403 --> 45:06.370 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
religious views.

45:06.404 --> 45:08.072 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
But kids are still innocent.

45:08.105 --> 45:13.210 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, if we can succeed at putting
children
together, getting children to
shake hands,

45:13.244 --> 45:19.450 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
look into each other's eyes,
have that socialization
in where they can engage and
touch each other

45:19.483 --> 45:24.655 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
