that child becomes
a mayor or a commissioner or is
put in a position,

45:24.689 --> 45:29.894 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
he or she has an experience or
have had an
experience with African-American
youth.

45:29.927 --> 45:35.800 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, using chess as a tool to
bring kids together,
we do it through chess and
pizza, chess and

45:35.833 --> 45:38.636 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
