to whoop up
on the police officers through
chess, but

47:30.915 --> 47:32.717 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
all in positive interaction.

47:32.750 --> 47:37.655 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHARLAYNE HUNTER-GAULT: So, for
communities
where they don't have a chess
master, or even

47:37.688 --> 47:41.058 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
a griot, are there lessons
beyond chess, do
you think?

47:41.092 --> 47:44.628 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
When you they have these
divisions, how do
you bridge the gaps?

47:44.662 --> 47:47.298 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
LEMUEL LAROCHE: By bringing
people together.

47:47.331 --> 47:48.632 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
CHARLAYNE HUNTER-GAULT: How?

47:48.666 --> 47:51.635 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
You can't just stand on the
street and you
say, you all come.

47:51.669 --> 47:53.003 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
We're going to get together
tonight.

47:53.037 --> 47:56.207 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LEMUEL LAROCHE: By building what
we have built
locally in Athens.

47:56.240 --> 47:58.175 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
It was a process.

47:58.209 --> 48:04.281 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
You first have to allow those
who are in positions
of power to engage with people
who are affected

48:04.315 --> 48:07.952 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
by policies that are being
joined.

48:07.985 --> 48:14.058 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, to get both in a room, we
have helped
to strengthen that process
through our annual

48:14.091 --> 48:15.893 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
