You Go, There
They Are."

50:48.979 --> 50:53.050 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ANNABELLE GURWITCH, Author,
"Wherever You
Go, There They Are": When my
sister and I

50:53.083 --> 50:59.556 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
