insurances to detangle.

50:59.590 --> 51:04.495 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We wanted them to move nearer to
us, but they
needed to stay close to their
doctors.

51:04.528 --> 51:09.633 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Now, the aging-at-home option
has been touted
as a cost saver, but it doesn't
address the

51:09.667 --> 51:14.338 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
